{"tid":690113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"社運人士文化中心外悼念六四事件 百人出席","createTime":"2018-06-04T15:02:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T15:19:47.000Z","uid":28366,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7db1480158b14bd41f86de5b84276c842df9a905","tid":690113,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T15:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/230213_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F230213_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=85eca433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/230215_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F230215_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=980ecd36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n六四事件29周年，有社運人士晚上在尖沙咀文化中心露天廣場舉辦六四悼念活動，近100人出席。活動開始前，有警員及康文署人員上前警告負責人，指活動未獲批「不反對通知書」，建議他們移師到柏麗大道，但負責人未有理會。<br />\n<br />\n參與者先默哀1分鐘，並讀出3首諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波遺孀劉霞所寫的詩，又在現場一個雕像擺放電子蠟燭，期間有人舉起「香港獨立」旗幟，數十名警員及康文署職員在場戒備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1011949\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_341%26itemid%3D1011949&d=itjYovnSLJFyDy%2BRQv9H0J4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=c2ced32a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1011949</a>"},{"pid":"49ab1720b7d5a629d3c30cc316c3419263cf07b7","tid":690113,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T15:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52162b0709dc214965029c6439bd86e08c1b59df","tid":690113,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T15:08:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e4eea5